item.title: CVE-2022-2269|2024-08-03T00:32:09.316Z -- unknown -- website%20file%20changes%20monitor
item.description: The Website File Changes Monitor WordPress plugin before 1.8.3 does not sanitise and escape user input before using it in a SQL statement via an action available to users with the manage_options capability (by default admins), leading to an SQL injection
